{
  "texts": [
    "Group 2 (TDD + GPT):",
    " Participants explicitly follow TDD methodology.",
    " Participants must explicitly write tests first, implementing code to pass tests using GPT assistance.",
    "In both groups, participants will document their GPT interactions by copying their entire GPT sessions (prompts and responses) into a provided Word document, enabling detailed qualitative analysis of interactions.",
    "We aim to recruit approximately 40-50 participants drawn from the second year \"Concepts in AI\" module at Cardiff Metropolitan University."
  ]
}